        <mxCell id="step3-process" value="1. Parse MRZ (Document Number + DOB + Expiry)&#xa;2. Derive K_seed via SHA-1&#xa;3. Calculate K_enc and K_mac (3DES keys)&#xa;4. Mutual Authentication → Session Keys" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontColor=#276749;" vertex="1" parent="1">
